  "tactics": "The Blood Knight is a relentless frontline tank, leveraging its high AC and immunities to draw enemy fire. It uses its Multiattack to quickly heal itself with the Bloodforged Blade. When surrounded or facing clustered enemies, it utilizes the Blood Corruption Blast to deal mass damage and weaken foes by reducing their maximum HP, accepting the temporary reduction to its own power for battlefield control. It prioritizes using its Bloodforged Shield reaction against critical attacks or high-level spells to maintain its longevity."
